{"tid":1462162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合國：港警違反國際標準及規範","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:41:54.000Z","uid":154277,"like":241,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"4b3f4ca5b6d8f40b27f5bca009bd9ca28b842e94","tid":1462162,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:05:35.000Z","msg":"聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處發言人Rupert Colville剛剛在瑞士日內瓦見記者，回應香港暴力衝突及警方執法情況。<br />\n.<br />\n聯合國人權理事會表示，已檢視可信證據，香港執法人員使用低致命武器（less lethal weapons）時違反國際標準及規範。例如，執法人員在不同場合分別向人群、在密閉空間及直接向個別示威者施放催淚彈，有機會造成嚴重傷亡。理事會促請香港政府立即調查相關事件，確保執法人員遵守武力指引，有需要時應修改武力指引，確保符合國際標準。<br />\n.<br />\n理事會促請特區政府保持克制，確保市民和平表達訴求的權利受保障，確保執法人員使用是合乎比例武力應對暴力行為。<br />\n.<br />\n人權事務高級專員辦事處關注香港近日暴力升級事件，譴責任何形式的暴力或破壞公物行為，促請集會人士和平示威，又呼籲特區政府與市民公開對話，尋求解決問題方法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGENEVA, Aug 13 (Reuters) - United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights Michelle Bachelet urged Hong Hong authorities on Tuesday to exercise restraint and investigate evidence of its forces firing tear gas at protesters in ways banned by international law.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;Officials can be seen firing tear gas canisters into crowded, enclosed areas and directly at individual protesters on multiple occasions, creating a considerable risk of death or serious injury,&rdquo; Bachelet said in a statement.</span><br />\n<br />\nChina&rsquo;s comments on Monday about &ldquo;sprouts of terrorism&rdquo; emerging in Hong Kong are not helpful and risk inflaming the situation, her spokesman Rupert Colville told a news briefing. (Reporting by Stephanie Nebehay Editing by Peter Graff)<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://app3.rthk.hk/special/pau/article.php?aid=3659&amp;fbclid=IwAR0sZAOpjut3wgPAy8C2D4YulVL5GLURCk5-tlDBNgTeH0nQrZq6o3J6mfw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp3.rthk.hk%2Fspecial%2Fpau%2Farticle.php%3Faid%3D3659%26fbclid%3DIwAR0sZAOpjut3wgPAy8C2D4YulVL5GLURCk5-tlDBNgTeH0nQrZq6o3J6mfw&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvhR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=2a8dcbeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://app3.rthk.hk/special/pau/article.php?aid=3659&amp;fbclid=IwAR0sZAOpjut3wgPAy8C2D4YulVL5GLURCk5-tlDBNgTeH0nQrZq6o3J6mfw</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/hongkong-protests-un/un-urges-hong-kong-to-use-restraint-investigate-excessive-force-idUSL8N25929I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fhongkong-protests-un%2Fun-urges-hong-kong-to-use-restraint-investigate-excessive-force-idUSL8N25929I&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvhR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=234273ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fhongkong-protests-un%2Fun-urges-hong-kong-to-use-restraint-investigate-excessive-force-idUSL8N25929I&h=8433b253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/hongkong-protests-un/un-urges-hong-kong-to-use-restraint-investigate-excessive-force-idUSL8N25929I</a><br />\n."},{"pid":"3a17105ccdd2ff2859c9bc0f8d041b3d752ee0b2","tid":1462162,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:06:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f21981aaa92177a0bab316a8d3e929f0bac1818c","tid":1462162,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26ccba6f6ce0dcc53e36c492749c1514b7b9111","tid":1462162,"uid":35667,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:07:12.000Z","msg":"口交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0639b4113e7ab04b76412b7dcda4280474b195fc","tid":1462162,"uid":49315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:07:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"986544ff5eba6534d0f1bed2298dcb2543f3e528","tid":1462162,"uid":215734,"like":0,"disl